# Meross MQTT Bridge — Environment Variables
# -------------------------------------------
# SECRET_KEY is auto-generated on first boot by the GUI container
# and saved to config/.env on the shared config volume.
#
# To generate manually:
#   python3 -c "from cryptography.fernet import Fernet; print(Fernet.generate_key().decode())"
#
# Then create config/.env with:
#   SECRET_KEY=<your-generated-key>
#
# Back up config/.env separately from config/config.yaml.
# Neither file is useful for decryption without the other.
